text: Ceriel Oosthout (born 27 September 1984 in Deventer) is a Dutch footballer who currently plays for FC Hilversum in the Dutch third division. ==Club career== He had a spell at Eerste Divisie side Go Ahead Eagles. His only previous club was SV Colmschate '33, where he played in the youth. ==External Links / References== *Voetbalnext- Ceriel Oosthout Category:1984 births Category:Living people Category:Sportspeople from Deventer Category:Go Ahead Eagles players Category:Eerste Divisie players Category:Association football midfielders Category:Dutch footballers Category:FC Hilversum players
